<lyrics>[V1]
 1- jyt lk wạ̉nạ mdywn .. sddt ly dywny
 jyt lk wạ̉nạ ạ̉ʿmy̱ .. ftḥt ly ʿywny
 ạlqrạr- (ạ̹nt ḥbyb qlby .. ạ̉rwḥ lmyn gẖyrk)2
 (ạ̹nt yswʿ rby .. ạ̉rkʿ wạ̉ṣly lk)2
 2- jyt lk wạ̉nạ kẖạṭy .. gẖfrt ly dẖnwby
 ṭhrt ly qlby .. wstrt kl ʿywby
 3- jyt lk wạ̉nạ mjrwḥ .. ḍmdt ly jrwḥy
 wbrwḥk ạlqdws .. ạ̉nʿsẖt fyã rwḥy
 4- jyt lk wạ̉nạ mryḍ .. ṭlbt tsẖfyny
 ṭybtny fy ạlḥạl .. mn mrḍy wạ̉nyny</lyrics>
<title>jyt lk wạ̉nạ mdywn</title>
</song>